{"id": "ChIJV_w_syh8hYAROFYl9TYxCII", "rating": 4.6, "priceLevel": "PRICE_LEVEL_INEXPENSIVE", "userRatingCount": 486, "displayName": {"text": "Yogurt Park", "languageCode": "en"}, "editorialSummary": {"text": "Long-running (since 1977)  shop, open late, offering frozen yogurt in simple digs.", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJV_w_syh8hYAROFYl9TYxCII/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT210cFpuY3phRTltVUZoQ01WSnRTRTR4Yldob1ZuYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 weeks ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "We stumbled upon this place while it was packed with a long line, and we couldn’t resist trying their desserts. Unfortunately, they had limited options on a Saturday night, so we settled for the Dutch chocolate. The service was friendly, and the yougurt was incredibly delicious! It was a generous portion for a small size, and the toppings elevated each bite. I opted for the cookie and chocolate chip toppings, and it was absolutely divine on a hot day. This place is a must-try!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "We stumbled upon this place while it was packed with a long line, and we couldn’t resist trying their desserts. Unfortunately, they had limited options on a Saturday night, so we settled for the Dutch chocolate. The service was friendly, and the yougurt was incredibly delicious! It was a generous portion for a small size, and the toppings elevated each bite. I opted for the cookie and chocolate chip toppings, and it was absolutely divine on a hot day. This place is a must-try!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Jagadeesh Rahul", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/100043892610065974009/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLLsSvwVuyRx5XZ2vxt5QEavjwwxRPE-uAKFhViHexiMwo2uQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba7"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-17T06:25:32.578963046Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT210cFpuY3phRTltVUZoQ01WSnRTRTR4Yldob1ZuYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT210cFpuY3phRTltVUZoQ01WSnRTRTR4Yldob1ZuYxAB!2m1!1s0x80857c28b33ffc57:0x82083136f5255638"}, {"name": "places/ChIJV_w_syh8hYAROFYl9TYxCII/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21veWRuUmFOWGsxZGxKV05VOU9OVnBvVUZBMFdHYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 weeks ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "Very popular place. While strolling around UC Berkley campus in summer, we saw that every other person is eating this. Our curiosity lead us to this place. We ordered their most popular Rocky Road flavor, Overall, the icecream was good but too heavy to eat it all.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Very popular place. While strolling around UC Berkley campus in summer, we saw that every other person is eating this. Our curiosity lead us to this place. We ordered their most popular Rocky Road flavor, Overall, the icecream was good but too heavy to eat it all.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Anshul Soni", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/110967740705679626605/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLHKgeRZSb2yVoD3iBe5v04ukUApIQ7KnXvlOVQI2Z_dZxpqAsX=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-20T01:47:24.898196956Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21veWRuUmFOWGsxZGxKV05VOU9OVnBvVUZBMFdHYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21veWRuUmFOWGsxZGxKV05VOU9OVnBvVUZBMFdHYxAB!2m1!1s0x80857c28b33ffc57:0x82083136f5255638"}, {"name": "places/ChIJV_w_syh8hYAROFYl9TYxCII/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25aM1Z6QmtOMU5NUlhGbGNVaE1ZblZ6VUZodE5XYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Amazing ice cream! I loved the way they layered all the toppings. Would highly recommend to anybody in the area.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Amazing ice cream! I loved the way they layered all the toppings. Would highly recommend to anybody in the area.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Cameron Petinak", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/105342786541200075407/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWW2oIw0D7_u8EbaEomZJtca4aKtiey7TVEm0XOiggiR4_PKUXH=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-03-02T00:37:22.457959532Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25aM1Z6QmtOMU5NUlhGbGNVaE1ZblZ6VUZodE5XYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25aM1Z6QmtOMU5NUlhGbGNVaE1ZblZ6VUZodE5XYxAB!2m1!1s0x80857c28b33ffc57:0x82083136f5255638"}, {"name": "places/ChIJV_w_syh8hYAROFYl9TYxCII/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tSQ2MyRXRUMGh0WkZwRVowTTFlRFZJWkRGTU5IYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 weeks ago", "rating": 2, "text": {"text": "I love yogurt park so much. And I don’t want to be rude because I really do love this place. But my sister ordered a chocolate flavor with cookie dough and it was her first time and was so excited because I rave about it all the time. She took one bite and immediately knew something was off. She started swelling up and could barely talk to the point where she had to sit on the floor and use her epi pen. She didn’t order anything that would have peanuts so I went back to ask the staff. When I asked one of the staff members they seemed really indifferent and overall tired of their job which is fair I can get that. But nothing was done to resolve the issue. No refund no nothing, I don’t expect a refund but I do expect some kind action to make it right. They told me that they don’t cross contaminate and that they have a sign about allergies ( which you can BARELY) see from the window. Like please your customer literally got such a bad allergic reaction to the point where an epi pen is used and yall couldn’t care less. No shade to the staff I respect the hustle, but management should do more for customers that are put in health emergencies….. because of their product….", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I love yogurt park so much. And I don’t want to be rude because I really do love this place. But my sister ordered a chocolate flavor with cookie dough and it was her first time and was so excited because I rave about it all the time. She took one bite and immediately knew something was off. She started swelling up and could barely talk to the point where she had to sit on the floor and use her epi pen. She didn’t order anything that would have peanuts so I went back to ask the staff. When I asked one of the staff members they seemed really indifferent and overall tired of their job which is fair I can get that. But nothing was done to resolve the issue. No refund no nothing, I don’t expect a refund but I do expect some kind action to make it right. They told me that they don’t cross contaminate and that they have a sign about allergies ( which you can BARELY) see from the window. Like please your customer literally got such a bad allergic reaction to the point where an epi pen is used and yall couldn’t care less. No shade to the staff I respect the hustle, but management should do more for customers that are put in health emergencies….. because of their product….", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Alezeh Sajid", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/117918019897741431578/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJwaWIbTwXFoHq2QWL7V57Tx8WOV5Az77THBqdzHNT_CwXNwA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-23T02:55:08.715861712Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tSQ2MyRXRUMGh0WkZwRVowTTFlRFZJWkRGTU5IYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tSQ2MyRXRUMGh0WkZwRVowTTFlRFZJWkRGTU5IYxAB!2m1!1s0x80857c28b33ffc57:0x82083136f5255638"}, {"name": "places/ChIJV_w_syh8hYAROFYl9TYxCII/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25OZlFqWlVkV2hxU21wUGQzUlBjSGhpU1ZoTFRWRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "9 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Review from an old time Yogurt Park customer: As good as ever only more expensive and without samples.  I was very happy after my indulgence and will be back! Peanut butter was always my favorite flavor.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Review from an old time Yogurt Park customer: As good as ever only more expensive and without samples.  I was very happy after my indulgence and will be back! Peanut butter was always my favorite flavor.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Susie Wyshak", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/108242834159095333585/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVrlu7Zs0bRkpwAr01Rf3o0iuoXWwOoq4c-RYtDi4WEzhnDbrw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2025-10-04T22:16:53.703060457Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25OZlFqWlVkV2hxU21wUGQzUlBjSGhpU1ZoTFRWRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25OZlFqWlVkV2hxU21wUGQzUlBjSGhpU1ZoTFRWRRAB!2m1!1s0x80857c28b33ffc57:0x82083136f5255638"}], "photos": [{"name": "places/ChIJV_w_syh8hYAROFYl9TYxCII/photos/AWCwydjyFJJmKVv38UJAtVocmjRtE2MOmgH3RAOv2ub1iHPBlzqSyXzg4NJV_lmXuZoAhF2KFIazI9MteGB0v0GLOCSYZaaVDHWNZKWQokwac3M4-cOkaAzFOK9TG28Wb0e1plYfYpkudJXy4NXau1LxfpGiGOKdpNrODBucHtaTUA-BXkbcbBG54Rz5aw4DZeWy-5_OfqXsDlzTGxXURugFm1ITQzshU519LfcmH1-qLXX6kevKgEuyQHfYZKFrcgfl32FdHx7rrgP8hTNQ75UZBqTS4l4zLpvThC7hetT7JdBisr-WtMtH_hsIjKcAgnYVIx2vSKibol32Hbw-bjspsQNnwTTDF5yr